Joining it to the existing Census tracts shapefile (in my example, named `ok_tracts`) requires a simple `INNER JOIN` based on the two common fields:

- [acs_14_5yr_b01003](https://daannguyen.cartodb.com/tables/acs_14_5yr_b01003):  `geo_id`
